<h1>Math Problems</h1>
<ol>
<li>2 + 2<input data-correct="4"></li>
<li>2 + 3<input data-correct="5"></li>
<li>2<sup>3</sup> <input data-correct="8"></li>
<li>2<sup>4</sup> <input data-correct="16"></li>
